description: Say hello to this 2017 bi-level home, perfectly situated on sought-after Thomas Park in South Boston. Boasting 3 beds, 2.5 baths, & off-street parking, this modern residence combines high-end finishes with smart home convenience. The heart of the home is a chef’s kitchen featuring white quartz countertops, a herringbone subway tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, a 6-burner gas range with professional hood, a wine fridge, and a large island with a waterfall edge. Custom pantry cabinets with pullouts offer exceptional storage, while a private deck off the kitchen is perfect for morning coffee. Retreat to the primary, complete with double closets & en-suite bath featuring marble tile, a double vanity, and a glass-enclosed shower. The second bed also includes its own en-suite bath & a generous closet, while the third bedroom is perfect for a guest room, nursery, home office or media room. Enjoy the convenience of in-unit laundry, surround sound tech controlling lights & climate.
